resources.string: locked but device is running a self-signed ROM

About: 
This application detects Magisk but just want to tell you that Magisk v23.0 was buggy, applications can easily detect Magisk so you should update it. Update Magisk to v24 can pass all detections.
Author: GitHub @canyie
Source code: https://github.com/canyie/MagiskKiller

This is a simple app to help you know if your Magisk is properly hidden by MagiskHide.

This app does not require any permissions.
All checks runs locally, and we will not and cannot send any data to the Internet.
